data.title: Files Extensions and File Type Definitions list
meta_keywords: file extension file type info information
data.meta_description: TrID file type file extension defs list
data.text:
This is the list of every file type and file extension recognized by TrID file identifier. Check the Forum for a detailed change log.

You are welcome to contribute with new defs: Send me them and you will be listed here!

Check the TrIDScan page for a quick How-To. Thanks!
